{"tid":1782570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［修復連儂牆計劃］每日一紙文宣","createTime":"2019-12-14T05:40:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T01:48:33.000Z","uid":334255,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6cf93cab2f05fc9e4ca665fb75ff9881f93bf494","tid":1782570,"uid":334255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T05:40:33.000Z","msg":"爬山半年，香港人創造咗好多有影響力嘅行動出嚟。其中造成極大影響嘅無疑係十八區連儂牆。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n影響之大令好多藍絲認識事實轉黃；<br />\n少接觸網絡媒介手足可以得到活動資訊；<br />\n澄清警謊及tvb假新聞；<br />\n解釋裝修原因；<br />\n視覺藝術效果等等。<br />\n簡單啲嚟講既可以俾手足圍爐回血，鞏固淺黃手足，亦可以令藍轉黃。港共頻頻急清各大連儂牆就係認證咗連儂牆嘅大成效，依家連共兵都向文宣方向發展。<br />\n<br />\n然而至今，連儂牆都未可以回復當初百花齊放之樣貌。最主要原因係冇人做！固然有手足keep住做緊嘢，但係更多人係食緊花生等睇靚靚文宣，包括小弟我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n手足礙於未試過，怕危險，怕醜，冇時間，組唔到隊等等嘅原因卻步，所以喺呢度我嘗試提供一個人人都貼到文宣嘅方法，務求每人每日貼一文宣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>工具</strong><br />\n1. 小型膠水樽，必備能大量擠出膠水及刷開膠水功能。<br />\n<br />\n2. 膠水，推薦牆紙膠水，五金鋪$30-$40。開偏水狀，防止唧唔出。<br />\n<br />\n3. 噴霧樽，有手足研究咗被撕文宣嘅不足之處（只要多一個簡單步驟就會令文宣難撕到 hi hi <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1663669），非必需改善工具。\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1663669），非必需改善工具。</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 文宣<br />\n來源：<br />\n。Tg文宣channel<br />\n。Facebook<br />\n。Instagram<br />\n。媒體新聞<br />\n。長輩圖生成器<br />\n。連登post (一啲連登po提出非常有用資訊，奈何只流傳於連登圍爐，最後埋沒於此。連登真係網絡孤島嚟嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，下次如果見到有好po, 不妨印出嚟通街貼啦)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>做法</strong><br />\n以上少少小工具，可以每日放喺個袋度，甚至得個褲袋都放到。每日返學放學返工放工出街食飯經過條街，就可以拎出支膠水同紙，擠膠水，搽開，貼係牆上，噴水（非必要），半分鐘就搞掂。<br />\n一來唔需要特登走去貼文宣，二來行動時間極短危險性自然大大降低。<br />\n呢個方法目的唔係要一個人貼好多張，係要好多個人只貼一張。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我要一日內香港街頭多幾萬張文宣！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>注意事項</strong><br />\n1. 以上方法令文宣唔再局限於舊有連儂牆位置。但太散落會冇人留意。<br />\n<br />\n2. 要20秒內快速完成，減低被點相被狗逗機會。寧願貼唔到/貼得衰，都唔要受傷被捕被抄牌被點相被捉走。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n口罩帽之類自行決定要唔要。唔好經常相同時間地點行動，儘量唔好係屋企附近貼。一定一定一定！要假設有便衣係附近，一眼關七！<br />\n<br />\n3. 有手足提議過牆以外嘅地方，例如櫈（[文宣要人] 連儂櫈<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1757361）。加啲創意同同理心，諗下邊度會有人駐足停留，即使貼一張都可能獲得意外之效。\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1757361）。加啲創意同同理心，諗下邊度會有人駐足停留，即使貼一張都可能獲得意外之效。</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（又例如：[和你勇文宣升級！] 解鎖新職業 &mdash; 郵差叔叔，速遞員！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1717313）\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1717313）</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 最重要，人身安全。唔好去太僻靜太夜太無人地方。組隊分工合作係十分理想，但係呢個方法就係俾大眾日常一貼，所以記緊自己注意安全。<br />\n<br />\n5. 如果你唔想留低任何證據，小心留意留下指紋或其他生物特徵。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. 值得睇：「行動post」連儂牆行動注意事項<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782418\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782418</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>危險性</strong><br />\n藍絲黑社會唔再講，仲要假設有便衣等你一貼就捉。視察環境，安全，半分鐘內貼好，走人。<br />\n有機會多咗隨機截人搜身，有支膠水都拉你。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>缺點</strong><br />\n1. 無法做到大型靚文宣，所以呢個方法唔係偏向觀賞性，而係資訊性。<br />\n2. 有被點相同攻擊嘅危險性。<br />\n<br />\n承先賢之志，燃革命之火。香港人，等我哋代替已經無法再行出嚟嘅手足重燃星星之火，將民主自由嘅意念燒開去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論可行性、成效及盲點。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他貼文宣攻略：<br />\n[詳盡戰術] [文宣]想復興連儂入嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1747421\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1747421</a>"},{"pid":"90f1020aa58f8d9bc4fba4bfe11ccceee1cb833b","tid":1782570,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T05:41:03.000Z","msg":"冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a42e8603a28f9e94a0a023715ddb1d92724bd7e6","tid":1782570,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T05:42:28.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBy the way, 借宣傳一下個APP<br />\n<br />\n香港地投票 - 黎投票啦！📊📊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1758886\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1758886</a>"},{"pid":"efb772bf4acfdeb645636e7e7d9834f67a683763","tid":1782570,"uid":251769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T05:44:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推行動post plz<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pyqyGMZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpyqyGMZ.jpg&h=2f6dc79b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4fc1dbbf6a21785669be63ad51b7efe392903b07","tid":1782570,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T05:48:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4815799d71227b5b6cfde9b5a5e4c1ff1c469283","tid":1782570,"uid":214621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T05:54:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5163a5d83a8421c28d73e6b69fc1d28cd5f90965","tid":1782570,"uid":334255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T06:28:07.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n唔到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n商量行動啦，咁好再睇好嬲好嬲po喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a004acc0ad52e42478786e6adada84a30b78f1c3","tid":1782570,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T04:03:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c94c83a962eedc89066052c8e2f0a5781c2aab81","tid":1782570,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T04:06:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b93649cf25300880c3fbd7f75195010ccb94e026","tid":1782570,"uid":24972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T04:08:51.000Z","msg":"推有用post啊！！！"},{"pid":"460616fe01a311fc703d0e9b5a2b2d7dc3c48ae1","tid":1782570,"uid":125026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T01:46:59.000Z","msg":"建議識印貼紙既手足應該派多啲畀人，畀佢地周圍貼，整連儂巴士、連儂廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c69366fdd0564f89bb60cb0bc383925f7300005","tid":1782570,"uid":125026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"460616fe01a311fc703d0e9b5a2b2d7dc3c48ae1","tid":1782570,"uid":125026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T01:46:59.000Z","msg":"建議識印貼紙既手足應該派多啲畀人，畀佢地周圍貼，整連儂巴士、連儂廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T01:47:54.000Z","msg":"比較多資訊性既可以印喺大Label紙，隨身袋住，見有空位就貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e43c37bf824ac711e65636a3b1b3d511f03b73b2","tid":1782570,"uid":301067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T01:48:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}